data.description: Welcome to your beautiful move-in ready home in highly desirable Castle Rock's Founder Village. This home boosts a beautiful floor plan, with 6 bedroom, 4 bathroom, 3 car garage, this home gives you plenty of space for the entire family! Main floor has a bedroom and full bath with a beautiful formal living room, formal dinning room and a laundry room. Vaulted high ceiling in the main family room with fireplace, lots of natural light and a beautiful open staircase. Enjoy cooking in the beautiful inviting kitchen that leads you right out to your beautiful private yard oasis that has beautiful plants that grow every year! Upstairs includes a Master bedroom with 5PC bathroom, 2 additional bedrooms, full bath and walk-in closets. The Fully finished basement has 2 additional bedrooms and 1 full bath giving enough space and privacy for all. This home has been well cared and thoughtfully updated with New Furnace & AC (2021), New Roof, updated kitchen cabinets, main floor has beautiful vinyl planks that are water resistance and basement has new flooring, New gutters (2020), New exterior paint (2020), beautiful landscape front and back of the house. Close to shopping and dinning, welcome to your new home!
